{"tid":1846141,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[國際戰線] 請求美國向中共同港共施壓，立即封鎖中港邊境保護美國85000個在港僑民","createTime":"2020-01-27T13:23:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T20:29:12.000Z","uid":270506,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"86e61c305eca3766942cac3509f527910431540b","tid":1846141,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:23:42.000Z","msg":"大家唔好唔記得我地可以從國際戰線向港共施壓。<br />\n美國喺香港有<strong>85000</strong>僑民，要派專機撤僑起碼要派<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&gt;200</span></span>班機，或者派n艘救援艦黎接走，基本上<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>無可能</strong></span>。<br />\n而家港共依然開放邊境放病人落黎，仲要免費醫佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，一旦疫症喺社區爆發，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">85000個美國僑民嘅健康就會受到威脅</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n各位國際戰線同twitter手足，係時候做嘢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，請求美國向中共同港共施壓，要求中共港共盡一切措施有效保護美國僑民嘅健康同安全，包括實施嚴格邊境管制，禁制所有中國大陸人士進入香港！<br />\n<br />\nTwitter：<br />\nNCM Yue<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SolomonYue\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSolomonYue&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5nqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=5a197ba7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SolomonYue</a><br />\n美國國務院<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/StateDept\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStateDept&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5nqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=5eaf5744\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/StateDept</a><br />\n美國駐港總領事館<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/USAinHKMacau\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUSAinHKMacau&d=gjA94EiKSJsk9JMrtOnM5nqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=5a3ccab8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/USAinHKMacau</a><br />\n<br />\nFb：<br />\n美國駐港總領事館<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/USAinHKMacau/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FUSAinH