auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eNxNpS</a><br />\nP牌無得推，得閒就入去推"},{"pid":"18f68aeb4fa911e5978af08a44ff72313cc3acdc","tid":1846141,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:28:11.000Z","msg":"推埋你"},{"pid":"f1f14bb45223fd4c2bbff78d2f648ad4da0fc0c3","tid":1846141,"uid":37516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:04:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9bcef73467b4507b116a17e57b8900d880523444","tid":1846141,"uid":297453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T17:37:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"355dee6cb5f26c50a46826b68c3b3b3404cdfdb5","tid":1846141,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:47:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"129a6f3f20000af67ce1a43c9a4062d5f2a28248","tid":1846141,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:48:18.000Z","msg":"黎明行動送頭<br />\n港島遊行集會送頭<br />\n深夜整連儂牆送頭<br />\n派傳單都會畀藍絲割肚不了<br />\n<br />\n而家我哋打旗號叫政府封關阻肺炎呀<br />\n民建聯都唔會夠膽出聲反對啦 粉嶺單野政府都hea應啦<br />\n<br />\n另外想問工會過咗咁多個月有幾多人入咗會？<br />\n全民大三罷？<br />\n唔好話無限期啦 就算一日 短期內我都睇唔出我哋有咩條件做得到 到時幾多生化人入咗關？再搞無限期三罷已經遲<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">因為到時已經有唔少香港人奶咗野 咁醫護仲點罷工呀</span><br />\n<br />\n醒下啦送頭<br />\n你話畀我知唔送頭仲可以點"},{"pid":"f6c2b945f3109a0151409c123d26566197a7fe7e","tid":1846141,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:56:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"134bf5700a381b7258e0dfba3537259cc380562b","tid":1846141,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T18:58:03.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"75c09924fe8c78df6297f826211a9939216dc69e","tid":1846141,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:03:42.000Z","msg":"我希望大家同我一齊嗌!! 嗌到大陸都一齊嗌!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1846888\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1846888</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>抗疫保命<br />\n推翻政權</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dbe650d6140e16b8fbbe85e1f76b60991c970fd","tid":1846141,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:15:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a566722d89608b48a758af880ee2e4906d9acb6","tid":1846141,"uid":296622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T19:49:23.000Z","msg":"緊急國際戰線：唔封關證明冇自治，要求美國制裁<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eNPpNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eNPpNS</a><br />\n<br />\n去美國國會議員、國務院的twitter留言，話港府不對中國封關，足以證明香港係完全冇自治，咁美國應該要取消對香港的優待。亦希望我要攬炒、大專遊說團、眾志gphone等快快幫拖。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住要講：香港不對中國封關，死的，不只是香港人，還會是全世界。</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1426a86a8df818ded5fd4ed19d8259d4107134ae","tid":1846141,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T21:15:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e6e65a0b7d48712948cc5d6f68f46957594d5f01","tid":1846141,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T21:16:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fd79c1aed60dea11a01352dc4753c6cd2a02cd50","tid":1846141,"uid":38734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T00:28:55.000Z","msg":"Push push push<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca9e42d1464e3d064e3813a545f87d7ceca429dd","tid":1846141,"uid":338654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-